    <h2 class="quote">"People at OPOWER love going out and being active.  DC is a great place for that, whether it's running on Rock Creek Park or a night out in Dupont Circle."</h2>
    <h3>Ran Nussbacher, Director, Client Solutions</h3>

    <div class="large-text space-bottom">
        
        <p>The DC Metro Area offers a wide array of opportunities for OPOWER employees. We come from all over the world and are at all different states of life, so we’re into everything from getting a drink at a craft beer house in the District to spending time at the dog park in Arlington, Va.</p>
                
